@nuclear112 wrote:

Thanks

slightly darker text
You can edit the yellow text by clicking on Advanced -> Skin -> Run
One suggestion though. Make more textfields for messages and then have it say them randomly? Unless that's what the multi-message is, I'm not sure because multi-message isn't working.

Yes the multi-message box is going to make it so you can have a list of messages to be typed, and you will be able to choose what order to type them in random/top to bottom/bottom to top. I just wanted to release a quick version of the AutoTalker just to get people more familiar with NucBot. She be enabled in the next couple of versions coming out.

Can't wait to see your Auto-miner. (Don't forget the anti-randoms!)

The first release will probably not have all the anti-randoms but the final release will probably have all the anti-randoms. It will just take some time to perfect all the randoms.
